genresAdvancedInfo.name: nopixel
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre of music is inspired by the popular Grand Theft Auto V roleplaying server, NoPixel. It features a blend of electronic and hip-hop beats, with lyrics that tell stories of the gritty underworld of the city. Nopixel music is characterized by its dark and moody sound, and its ability to transport listeners into the world of the game.
